query:
SELECT TOP 1 *,ar.Cd_AR as Cd_AR,ar.Descrizione as Descrizione_AR,ARLotto.DataScadenza as scadenza_lotto
from xWPCollo 
LEFT JOIN AR ON xWPCollo.Cd_AR = AR.Cd_AR 
LEFT JOIN ARLotto ON ARLotto.Cd_AR = AR.Cd_AR and ARLotto.Cd_ARLotto = xWPCollo.xLotto
WHERE Nr_Collo = [param1]
